{"id":188,"parent_id":186,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":188,"title":"Philippians 2","subtitle":"","short_title":"Philip.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 2"],[".studySummary",["i","Saints should be of one mind and one spirit—Every knee will bow to Christ—Saints must work out their salvation—Paul faces martyrdom with joy."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.1","order":"03.13.002.20649"},["b","1"],"If",["i","there be"],"therefore any consolation in Christ, if any comfort of love, if any fellowship of the Spirit, if any",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"bowels and mercies"],","],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.2","order":"03.13.002.20650"},["b","2"],"Fulfil ye my joy, that ye be likeminded, having the same",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"love"],",",["i","being"],"of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"one"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_2c"},"accord"],", of one mind."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.3","order":"03.13.002.20651"},["b","3"],["i","Let"],"nothing",["i","be done"],"through",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"strife"],"or vainglory; but in lowliness of mind let each",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"esteem"],"other better than themselves."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.4","order":"03.13.002.20652"},["b","4"],"Look not every man on his own things, but every man also on the things of others."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.5","order":"03.13.002.20653"},["b","5"],"Let this mind be in you, which was also in Christ Jesus:"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.6","order":"03.13.002.20654"},["b","6"],"Who, being in the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"form"],"of God, thought it not robbery to be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"equal"],"with God:"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.7","order":"03.13.002.20655"},["b","7"],"But made himself of no reputation, and took upon him the form of a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"servant"],", and was made in the likeness of men:"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.8","order":"03.13.002.20656"},["b","8"],"And being found in",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"fashion"],"as a man, he",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"humbled"],"himself, and became",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_8c"},"obedient"],"unto",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_8d"},"death"],", even the",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_8e"},"death"],"of the cross."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.9","order":"03.13.002.20657"},["b","9"],"Wherefore God also hath highly",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"exalted"],"him, and given him a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"name"],"which is above every name:"],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.10","order":"03.13.002.20658"},["b","10"],"That at the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"name"],"of Jesus every",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"knee"],"should bow, of",["i","things"],"in heaven, and",["i","things"],"in earth, and",["i","things"],"under the earth;"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.11","order":"03.13.002.20659"},["b","11"],"And",["i","that"],"every tongue should confess that Jesus Christ",["i","is"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"Lord"],", to the glory of God the Father."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.12","order":"03.13.002.20660"},["b","12"],"Wherefore, my beloved, as ye have always obeyed, not as in my presence only, but now much more in my absence,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"work"],"out your own",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"salvation"],"with fear and trembling."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.13","order":"03.13.002.20661"},["b","13"],"For it is God which worketh in you both to will and to do of",["i","his"],"good pleasure."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.14","order":"03.13.002.20662"},["b","14"],"Do all things without murmurings and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"disputings"],":"],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.15","order":"03.13.002.20663"},["b","15"],"That ye may be blameless and harmless, the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"sons"],"of God, without rebuke, in the midst of a crooked and perverse",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"nation"],", among whom ye",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_15c"},"shine"],"as lights in the world;"],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.16","order":"03.13.002.20664"},["b","16"],"Holding forth the word of life; that I may rejoice in the day of Christ, that I have not run in vain, neither laboured in vain."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.17","order":"03.13.002.20665"},["b","17"],"Yea, and if I be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"offered upon"],"the sacrifice and service of your faith, I joy, and rejoice with you all."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.18","order":"03.13.002.20666"},["b","18"],"For the same cause also do ye joy, and rejoice with me."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.19","order":"03.13.002.20667"},["b","19"],"But I trust in the Lord Jesus to send Timotheus shortly unto you, that I also may be of good comfort, when I know your state."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.20","order":"03.13.002.20668"},["b","20"],"For I have no man likeminded, who will naturally care for your state."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.21","order":"03.13.002.20669"},["b","21"],"For all",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"seek"],"their",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"own"],", not the things which are Jesus Christ’s."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.22","order":"03.13.002.20670"},["b","22"],"But ye know the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"proof"],"of him, that, as a son with the father, he hath served with me in the gospel."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.23","order":"03.13.002.20671"},["b","23"],"Him therefore I hope to send presently, so soon as I shall see how it will go with me."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.24","order":"03.13.002.20672"},["b","24"],"But I trust in the Lord that I also myself shall come shortly."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.25","order":"03.13.002.20673"},["b","25"],"Yet I supposed it necessary to send to you",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"Epaphroditus"],", my brother, and companion in labour, and fellowsoldier, but your messenger, and he that ministered to my wants."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.26","order":"03.13.002.20674"},["b","26"],"For he longed after you all, and was full of heaviness, because that ye had heard that he had been sick."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.27","order":"03.13.002.20675"},["b","27"],"For indeed he was sick nigh unto death: but God had mercy on him; and not on him only, but on me also, lest I should have sorrow upon sorrow."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.28","order":"03.13.002.20676"},["b","28"],"I sent him therefore the more carefully, that, when ye see him again, ye may rejoice, and that I may be the less sorrowful."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.29","order":"03.13.002.20677"},["b","29"],"Receive him therefore in the Lord with all",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_29a"},"gladness"],"; and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_29b"},"hold"],"such in",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_29c"},"reputation"],":"],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.30","order":"03.13.002.20678"},["b","30"],"Because for the work of Christ he was nigh unto death, not regarding his life, to supply your",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_30a"},"lack"],"of service toward me."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.1a","order":"03.13.002.20679"},["b","1a"],["span.small","GR"],"tender affections of the heart and compassion."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.2a","order":"03.13.002.20681"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/benevolence"},"TG Benevolence"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.2b","order":"03.13.002.20683"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/unity"},"TG Unity"],"."],["div",{"id":"2c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.2c","order":"03.13.002.20685"},["b","2c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/12.10.10-18"},"Rom. 12:10 (10–18)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/7.18.18-21"},"Moses 7:18 (18–21)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.3a","order":"03.13.002.20687"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/strife"},"TG Strife"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.3b","order":"03.13.002.20689"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/humility"},"TG Humility"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/love"},"Love"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/respect"},"Respect"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.6a","order":"03.13.002.20691"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-body-of-corporeal-nature"},"TG God, Body of, Corporeal Nature"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/man-physical-creation-of"},"Man, Physical Creation of"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.6b","order":"03.13.002.20693"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-relationships-with-the-father"},"TG Jesus Christ, Relationships with the Father"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.7a","order":"03.13.002.20695"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/53.4.3-7"},"Isa. 53:4 (3–7)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/8.9.8-15"},"2 Cor. 8:9 (8–15)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/2.9"},"Heb. 2:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.8a","order":"03.13.002.20697"},["b","8a"],["span.small","GR"],"outward appearance."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.8b","order":"03.13.002.20699"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/humility"},"TG Humility"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/meek"},"Meek"],"."],["div",{"id":"8c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.8c","order":"03.13.002.20701"},["b","8c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/50.5"},"Isa. 50:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"8d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.8d","order":"03.13.002.20703"},["b","8d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-death-of"},"TG Jesus Christ, Death of"],"."],["div",{"id":"8e","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.8e","order":"03.13.002.20705"},["b","8e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-atonement-through"},"TG Jesus Christ, Atonement through"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.9a","order":"03.13.002.20707"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/exaltation"},"TG Exaltation"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.9b","order":"03.13.002.20709"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/mal/1.11"},"Mal. 1:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/1.4"},"Heb. 1:4"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/name"},"TG Name"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.10a","order":"03.13.002.20711"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/27.31"},"Mosiah 27:31"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/76.110.106-111"},"D&C 76:110 (106–11)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.104.103-104"},"88:104 (103–4)"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.10b","order":"03.13.002.20713"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/45.23"},"Isa. 45:23"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/14.11"},"Rom. 14:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.11a","order":"03.13.002.20715"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-messiah"},"TG Jesus Christ, Messiah"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.12a","order":"03.13.002.20717"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/34.37"},"Alma 34:37"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/9.27"},"Morm. 9:27"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/good-works"},"TG Good Works"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.12b","order":"03.13.002.20719"},["b","12b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/salvation"},"TG Salvation"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.14a","order":"03.13.002.20721"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/disputations"},"TG Disputations"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.15a","order":"03.13.002.20723"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sons-and-daughters-of-god"},"TG Sons and Daughters of God"],"."],["div",{"id":"15b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.15b","order":"03.13.002.20725"},["b","15b"],["span.small","GR"],"generation."],["div",{"id":"15c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.15c","order":"03.13.002.20727"},["b","15c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/mission-of-early-saints"},"TG Mission of Early Saints"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.17a","order":"03.13.002.20729"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.8"},"1 Thes. 2:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/98.13"},"D&C 98:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.21a","order":"03.13.002.20731"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/apathy"},"TG Apathy"],"."],["div",{"id":"21b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.21b","order":"03.13.002.20733"},["b","21b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/10.24"},"1 Cor. 10:24"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.22a","order":"03.13.002.20735"},["b","22a"],["span.small","GR"],"trial."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.25a","order":"03.13.002.20737"},["b","25a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.18"},"Philip. 4:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"29a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.29a","order":"03.13.002.20739"},["b","29a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/cheerful"},"TG Cheerful"],"."],["div",{"id":"29b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.29b","order":"03.13.002.20741"},["b","29b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/5.13"},"1 Thes. 5:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"29c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.29c","order":"03.13.002.20743"},["b","29c"],["span.small","GR"],"honor."],["div",{"id":"30a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.30a","order":"03.13.002.20745"},["b","30a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.10"},"Philip. 4:10"],"."]]}
